Currently, there's no method to configure the Activity Stream to show the activity of the issues assigned to the current user.

The only alternative is to either place the user's username into the Activity Stream gadget (which probably would not show the activity by other users into the issue), or to place the issue key into the gadget (which would be hard and inefficient to do, especially if the assigned issues is a lot/changed constantly).

Hence, it would be useful to have some configuration that would allow the user to view their assigned issues in the activity stream.

