For example: users john and mike work in a company. John is a developer and Mike is a tester. Only John should be able to be the assignee of the issue while it is "In Progress" and only Mike could be the assignee when the issue is in "QA". For now, since they both have the *Assignable user* permission, they both can be the assignee in any step of the workflow.

